## Files Created

### 1. [crypto.ts](file:///c:/Users/ajmal_inv2bct/OneDrive/Desktop/web%20projects/spirox/apps/web/src/lib/crypto.ts) (NEW)

The core encryption engine.

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| Algorithm | AES-256-GCM (Authenticated Encryption) |
| Key Derivation | PBKDF2 with 100,000 iterations + SHA-256 |
| Key Source | Derived from `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` + app salt |
| IV | Random 12-byte IV per encryption (stored alongside ciphertext) |
| Output | Base64-encoded `IV || ciphertext || auth_tag` |

Key design decisions:
- The encryption key is **deterministic per deployment** (same key on every page load) but **unique per Supabase project** (different deployments can't decrypt each other's data).
- The key is cached in memory after first derivation to avoid re-running PBKDF2 on every read/write.

