### 3. [offlineAuth.ts](file:///c:/Users/ajmal_inv2bct/OneDrive/Desktop/web%20projects/spirox/apps/web/src/lib/offlineAuth.ts) (NEW)

The offline premium verification engine implementing the algorithm from [offline_auth_algorithm.md](file:///c:/Users/ajmal_inv2bct/OneDrive/Desktop/web%20projects/spirox/offline_auth_algorithm.md).

**Verification flowchart:**
```
App Opens → Token exists? → RSA signature valid? → Time moved forward? → Not expired? → PREMIUM ✅
     ↓ No          ↓ No              ↓ No                ↓ No
   FREE          FREE        TIME TAMPERING → FREE    EXPIRED → FREE
```

The RSA Public Key is hardcoded in the frontend. The corresponding Private Key will live on the Supabase Edge Function backend. A `createDevOfflineToken()` helper is included for testing.

